Maxtor Corp and U.S. DesignCorp &lt;USDC>, said they reached definitive agreement coveringthe acquisition of U.S. Design by Maxtor.    They said the arrangement, which is subject to a number ofconditions including U.S. Design shareholder approval, callsfor Maxtor to issue 12 mln dlrs worth of its own common stockin exchange for all of U.S. Design.    The number of Maxtor shares to be issued will be determinedby the average closing price of Maxtor stock over the 10trading day period prior to the day the acquisition becomeseffective, the companies also said. Reuter&#3;